Package com.jeanchampemont.gunip

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryByteParser
    A BinaryByteParser is a GenericUnitParser for binary units of information, from bytes to yobibyte.
    DecimalByteParser
    A DecimalByteParser is a GenericUnitParser for decimal units of information, from bytes to yottabyte.
    DurationParser
    A DurationParser is a GenericUnitParser for durations, from seconds to years.
    GenericUnitParser
    A Generic Unit Parser is a natural language parser to parse strings containing a sequence of tuples (value, unit), and convert it into a single value in a base unit.
    ImperialDistanceParser
    A ImperialDistanceParser is a GenericUnitParser for imperial distances, including inches, feet, yards and miles
    MetricDistanceParser
    A MetricDistanceParser is a GenericUnitParser for metric distances, from millimeters to kilometers.
    Unit
    A Unit is a list of patterns for that unit and its value in the base unit.
    UnitsBuilder
    Helper class to build a units table for a GenericUnitParser
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GenericUnitParserException
    An exception indicating that something went wrong during the parsing of a string.
